2. to check a number amstrong. Collin

pseudo:
Input num
originalNum = num
sum = 0
numDigits = number of digits in num
while num > 0
    digit = num % 10
    sum = sum + (digit ^ numDigits)
    num = num // 10
if originalNum == sum
    Print("The number is an Armstrong number")
else
    Print("The number is not an Armstrong number")


pseudo: routine
function IsArmstrong(num)
    originalNum = num
    sum = 0
    numDigits = number of digits in num
    while num > 0
        digit = num % 10
        sum = sum + (digit ^ numDigits)
        num = num // 10
    if originalNum == sum
        return True
    else
        return False

pseudo: test

procedure TestIsArmstrong()
    Input num
    if IsArmstrong(num)
        Print("The number is an Armstrong number")
    else
        Print("The number is not an Armstrong number")

